        <acqinfo encodinganalog="541">
            <p>Financial ledgers, daybooks, and other business records pertaining to the Lehrkind
                Coal and Ice Company were donated to Montana State University by Chan Libby of
                Livingston Montana on June 10, 1970. This collection was subsequently reported to
                the National Union Catalog of Manuscript Collections and assigned entry number
                79-676.</p>
        </acqinfo>
